      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">Welcome to 0451.eu, a digital archive dedicated to documenting and exploring easter eggs across various media platforms. This project aims to celebrate the creativity and hidden secrets within games, movies, and other digital content.</p>
        
