            <p class="text-lg">Hi, I'm David Girou, a software developer and easter egg enthusiast. I created this archive as part of my collection of projects under <a href="https://Cogilabs.eu/" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-300">Cogilabs.eu</a>, where I explore and document interesting aspects of digital culture.</p>
          </div>
